OL,3,CPhones to be banned in all Jersey
OL,4,Cschools after ITV News investigation
OL,6,FJersey's government will ban the use
OL,7,Fof mobile phones in all schools for
OL,8,Fstudents up to the end of Key Stage
OL,9,FFour.
OL,11,FA draft letter to parents and
OL,12,Fguardians, leaked to ITV Channel,
OL,13,Freveals that from the start of the
OL,14,Fnext academic year, all Government of
OL,15,FJersey schools and colleges will not
OL,16,Fallow pupils to use their phones at
OL,17,Fany time during the school day.
OL,19,FThe restriction covers break and
OL,20,Flunchtimes and all students, up to and
OL,21,Fincluding Year 11.
