OL,6,FThe new guidelines also say that
OL,7,Fschools "will not hesitate to contact
OL,8,Fpolice" if severe inappropriate
OL,9,Fcontent is accessed during school time.
OL,11,FParents are asked to "strongly
OL,12,Fconsider your decision to buy a
OL,13,Fsmartphone or give an old smartphone
OL,14,Fto your child".
OL,16,FThis follows an ITV Channel
OL,17,Finvestigation into the impact of
OL,18,Fsmartphones on young people, including
OL,19,Fan experiment where devices were taken
OL,20,Ffrom a group of students for two weeks.
