OL,3,CPhones to be banned in all Jersey
OL,4,Cschools after ITV News investigation
OL,6,F"Having a smartphone-free school day
OL,7,Fjust means kids will be free to learn
OL,8,Fwithout distraction and play and
OL,9,Fsocialise in real life. Play is a
OL,10,Ffundamental part of child development.
OL,11,FWithout it, we just don't develop the
OL,12,Fskills of innovation, imagination and
OL,13,Fsocialisation that we really need to
OL,14,Fsee in adults in our society.
OL,16,F"Many countries are looking into a
OL,17,Fsocial media ban for under-16-year-
OL,18,Folds, and we are seeing more and more
OL,19,Fharmful and negative effects of the
OL,20,Fimpact of social media on young
OL,21,Fpeople."
